high_descs: Move to the left side of the table.
Pick up the spoon from behind the lettuce.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the spoon inside of the mug,
Pick up the mug and close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk to the small black table to the right of the door.
Put the mug down on the black table to the left of the plate.
anns.task_desc: To put a spoon in a mug and put the mug on the black table.

high_descs: go to the left end of white table with lettuce
pick up spoon from behind lettuce on table
turn right, go to refrigerator
place spoon in white mug in refrigerator
pick up white mug with spoon, close refrigerator
turn around, go to black shelves at end of counter to the right
place mug on top left corner of black shelves
anns.task_desc: place mug with spoon on top of black shelves

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the metal spoon that is closest to the head of lettuce on the table.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the spoon in the white mug that is in the fridge.
Pick up the white mug with the spoon in it out of the fridge, then close the door.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk across the room to the wall, turn right again to face the small black shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the mug with the spoon in it on the front left corner of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on a black shelving unit.
